query:
INSERT INTO channel (
                id,
                channel_total,
                created_at, 
                updated_at
            )
            VALUES ($1, 1, NOW(), NOW())
            ON CONFLICT (id)
            DO UPDATE SET
                channel_total = channel.channel_total + 1,
                created_at = EXCLUDED.created_at,
                updated_at = NOW()
            RETURNING channel_total
